    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396640/extras/808fbd7293c4ba3fe8582edfdfbaef4d.poster.avif?t=1741316992\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396640/extras/808fbd7293c4ba3fe8582edfdfbaef4d.webm?t=1741316992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396640/extras/808fbd7293c4ba3fe8582edfdfbaef4d.mp4?t=1741316992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>·一款探索性且精美的动作游戏</strong></h2>使用不同的策略在许多独特的关卡中捕捉狐狸以取得成功。从悬崖上飞下来，猛扑毫无戒心的狐狸。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396640/extras/7a7e13c6689f09fe546756f602a7498b.poster.avif?t=1741316992\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396640/extras/7a7e13c6689f09fe546756f602a7498b.webm?t=1741316992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396640/extras/7a7e13c6689f09fe546756f602a7498b.mp4?t=1741316992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>・或者玩僵尸模式并逃离狐狸！</strong></h2>僵尸狐狸会来抓你，而且随着时间的推移，它们的速度会加快！通过在适当的时刻跳下山并悬挂滑翔，或者通过链接能量来跑得更快，你能生存多久？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396640/extras/f593fede325a249d6e497f2531d31623.poster.avif?t=1741316992\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396640/extras/f593fede325a249d6e497f2531d31623.webm?t=1741316992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396640/extras/f593fede325a249d6e497f2531d31623.mp4?t=1741316992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>·速度提升和记录时间</strong></h2>为每个级别设置高分，并解锁许多级别以在游戏中前进。两种模式都有自己的高分列表和关卡解锁。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396640/extras/548ecdeb48ad7ae5beb3ef213e708317.poster.avif?t=1741316992\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396640/extras/548ecdeb48ad7ae5beb3ef213e708317.webm?t=1741316992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396640/extras/548ecdeb48ad7ae5beb3ef213e708317.mp4?t=1741316992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>·有趣且多样的关卡设计</strong></h2>放大多种类型的关卡，从丛林到海洋再到分形，具有不同的外观和地理特征，允许采用不同的策略和方法。探索寻找狐狸聚集的祭坛，关注一只狐狸，因为它变得越来越快，获取能量，从山顶跳下后向前飞翔。",
